@page
@model FAQModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Frequently Asked Questions";
}

<div class="container">
    <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>

    <div class="faq-section">
        <h2>How does dark mode work?</h2>
        <p>Dark mode is automatically synced with your system settings. If your device is set to dark mode, the application will match your system preference. To change it, adjust your device's display settings, and the application will update automatically.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-section">
        <h2>How can I view my reflections?</h2>
        <p>You can view your reflections by navigating to the "Reflections" tab on the right column. Here you will find a list of all of your saved reflections. Click on any entry to view or edit it.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-section">
        <h2>How do I manage events in the calendar?</h2>
        <p>To manage events, go to the "Calendar" tab. You can click on any date to add an event, specifying details like title, time, and description. To edit or delete an event, simply click on the event in the calendar view.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-section">
        <h2>Can I print or export my calendar?</h2>
        <p>Yes, you can print your calendar. In the "Calendar" tab, click the "Options" button and select "Print calendar." This will open a printable view that you can save as a PDF directly.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-section">
        <h2>What should I do if I forget my login details?</h2>
        <p>If you forget your login details, click on the "Forgot Password" link on the login page. Enter your registered email address, and then there will be instructions on how to reset your password.</p>
    </div>
</div>
